		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I've been working on optimizing my SPC-700 DSP code again, and here are a few that use obscure functionality:
<br />
<br />Plok (drum samples will click at end if DSP doesn't cut last 9 samples off)
<br />Tetris vs. Dr. Mario (many waves will sound screwed up if DSP doesn't do BRR filtering correctly)

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


